776
00:37:38.990 --> 00:37:40.326
Weird.

777
00:37:40.459 --> 00:37:42.928
This ain't your fight.

778
00:37:42.994 --> 00:37:44.896
Kind of is.

779
00:37:44.963 --> 00:37:48.534
My father's fucked-up legacy
is my fucked-up legacy.

780
00:37:49.301 --> 00:37:51.870
I can't let him be forgotten.

781
00:37:52.638 --> 00:37:54.506
I think that's what he'd want.

782
00:37:55.240 --> 00:37:57.376
You know what he wouldn't want?

783
00:38:00.979 --> 00:38:03.349
I can take a good goddamn guess.

784
00:38:08.454 --> 00:38:09.955
[Mitch laughing]

785
00:38:10.021 --> 00:38:11.890
["On My Way Down"
by Trevor Hanks playing]

786
00:38:19.598 --> 00:38:21.833
[phone vibrates]

787
00:38:23.769 --> 00:38:26.505
* I know there's something
I could do right now *

788
00:38:26.638 --> 00:38:29.174
* And I could do it so proud
and I can do it... *

789
00:38:29.274 --> 00:38:31.643
-Skipper?
-Yeah.

790
00:38:31.743 --> 00:38:33.845
You find Armand?

791
00:38:33.979 --> 00:38:36.648
-No. but I spoke to his wife.
-How's Clara?

792
00:38:36.715 --> 00:38:38.517
I don't know how
the little douchebag did it.

793
00:38:38.617 --> 00:38:39.985
but. uh.
the "amends" shit worked.

794
00:38:40.085 --> 00:38:41.487
She's letting him see the kids.

795
00:38:41.587 --> 00:38:42.854
Well. mystery solved.

796
00:38:42.954 --> 00:38:45.190
Little road trip to the Rockies.
that's nice.

797
00:38:45.290 --> 00:38:47.325
You know what.
get her some flow--

798
00:38:47.426 --> 00:38:49.094
Look who I'm talking to.
You're not getting

799
00:38:49.194 --> 00:38:50.662
anyone any flowers anymore.

800
00:38:50.729 --> 00:38:52.798
Just get her some chocolate.
Can't screw that up.

801
00:38:52.864 --> 00:38:54.466
You're not gonna
let that go. are you?

802
00:38:54.533 --> 00:38:55.901
You know I'm not.

803
00:38:56.034 --> 00:38:58.236
* menacing music *

804
00:39:16.221 --> 00:39:17.656
Bigfoot.

805
00:39:17.723 --> 00:39:21.126
I'll stay.

806
00:39:21.226 --> 00:39:23.529
It's all right. I got this.

807
00:39:27.733 --> 00:39:30.502
Guess this means
you rejected my offer.

808
00:39:32.438 --> 00:39:35.206
Squandered opportunities.
Mr. Manfredi.

809
00:39:35.273 --> 00:39:37.375
Squandered opportunities.

810
00:39:37.476 --> 00:39:39.445
Why don't we have a seat
so I can tell you

811
00:39:39.578 --> 00:39:41.680
all the reasons I dislike you?

812
00:39:41.747 --> 00:39:43.949
Hmm? [chuckles]

813
00:39:53.291 --> 00:39:54.560
[Jace]
Come on. girl.

814
00:39:54.660 --> 00:39:56.394
Come on back in.
Dance with me.

815
00:39:56.495 --> 00:39:59.130
I don't want to dance with you.
I've been working all night.

816
00:39:59.264 --> 00:40:01.399
Just leave me the fuck alone.

817
00:40:03.602 --> 00:40:06.438
[Jace]
I know you want to be with me.

818
00:40:06.538 --> 00:40:08.339
Just go home.

819
00:40:16.682 --> 00:40:19.350
[grunts. gasps]
Jace. stop.

820
00:40:19.451 --> 00:40:20.886
You're hurting me.

821
00:40:20.986 --> 00:40:22.788
[grunts]

822
00:40:22.888 --> 00:40:24.523
[groaning]

823
00:40:26.892 --> 00:40:28.827
Was he anything to you?

824
00:40:28.960 --> 00:40:31.162
Not anymore.

825
00:40:32.163 --> 00:40:33.965
Aah!

826
00:40:34.933 --> 00:40:37.068
[groaning]

827
00:40:38.737 --> 00:40:40.405
What's your name?

828
00:40:40.472 --> 00:40:41.973
Cole.

829
00:40:51.783 --> 00:40:53.384
You okay?

830
00:40:53.485 --> 00:40:55.487
I am now.

831
00:40:58.824 --> 00:41:00.792
[car alarm chirps]

832
00:41:01.560 --> 00:41:03.862
* foreboding music *

833
00:41:05.463 --> 00:41:07.666
It is tedious.

834
00:41:07.766 --> 00:41:09.100
What is?

835
00:41:10.001 --> 00:41:11.469
Your flagrant disrespect

836
00:41:11.537 --> 00:41:13.004
for the way
things is done around here.

837
00:41:13.138 --> 00:41:16.542
Place my kin have called home
since before you were

838
00:41:16.642 --> 00:41:19.978
a misguided. filthy impulse
on your daddy's night off.

839
00:41:20.045 --> 00:41:22.814
Your kin should have
taught you manners.

840
00:41:22.914 --> 00:41:24.583
They taught me honor.

841
00:41:25.517 --> 00:41:27.619
So. given your intrusion...

842
00:41:29.287 --> 00:41:31.523
...I am obligated to destroy

843
00:41:31.623 --> 00:41:33.324
everything you have built

844
00:41:33.391 --> 00:41:35.126
and everyone you love.

845
00:41:35.193 --> 00:41:37.629
piece by piece. limb by limb.

846
00:41:37.696 --> 00:41:39.698
for my

847
00:41:39.798 --> 00:41:41.700
and my descendants' sake.

848
00:41:41.800 --> 00:41:43.368
Hmm.

849
00:41:44.302 --> 00:41:46.371
Let me give you
the facts of life.

850
00:41:47.539 --> 00:41:49.875
When it comes to money-- hey.

851
00:41:49.975 --> 00:41:51.877
money's money. Who cares?

852
00:41:51.977 --> 00:41:55.814
But when it comes to my people.
and you hurt them...

853
00:41:56.782 --> 00:42:00.552
...I will snatch away
your meaningless existence

854
00:42:00.652 --> 00:42:02.387
and everything that you

855
00:42:02.487 --> 00:42:04.890
and your descendants built.

856
00:42:04.990 --> 00:42:08.594
And the thing is.
I'm gonna have fun doing it.

857
00:42:09.394 --> 00:42:11.863
-Big talk.
-No.

858
00:42:11.930 --> 00:42:13.198
It's honest talk.

859
00:42:13.298 --> 00:42:15.333
I mean. let's face it.
you come in here.

860
00:42:15.400 --> 00:42:19.204
into my place. thinking
you're gonna make some kind

861
00:42:19.270 --> 00:42:21.472
of "fuck you" statement.

862
00:42:23.141 --> 00:42:25.043
But that ain't it. is it?

863
00:42:25.143 --> 00:42:26.377
Not really.

864
00:42:26.477 --> 00:42:29.080
You're here because
for the first time.

865
00:42:29.180 --> 00:42:31.082
maybe forever.

866
00:42:31.182 --> 00:42:33.418
you're scared.

867
00:42:33.518 --> 00:42:36.521
Your empire
is in danger. Dunmire.

868
00:42:36.588 --> 00:42:39.057
You have sway in Oklahoma.

869
00:42:39.157 --> 00:42:41.492
maybe three surrounding states.

870
00:42:41.593 --> 00:42:43.094
Whatever. Who gives a shit?

871
00:42:43.194 --> 00:42:47.065
But...
I'm gonna take it from you.

872
00:42:47.165 --> 00:42:49.835
All of it. Every bit.

873
00:42:49.935 --> 00:42:52.237
Then ten more. then 20 more.

874
00:42:52.337 --> 00:42:54.606
then the whole goddamn country

875
00:42:54.706 --> 00:42:56.374
on the back of what you

876
00:42:56.441 --> 00:42:59.544
and your kin built.

877
00:42:59.611 --> 00:43:01.613
You see.

878
00:43:01.713 --> 00:43:03.815
I'm just getting started.

879
00:43:03.949 --> 00:43:06.284
[chuckles]

880
00:43:06.417 --> 00:43:08.319
Well...

881
00:43:09.554 --> 00:43:13.591
Every man must do
two things alone. Manfredi.

882
00:43:14.425 --> 00:43:15.994
Got to do his own believing.

883
00:43:16.094 --> 00:43:18.630
even if that leads to hell.

884
00:43:18.730 --> 00:43:21.532
and he's got
to do his own dying.

885
00:43:24.135 --> 00:43:26.337
I'll be watching both.

886
00:43:33.411 --> 00:43:35.613
***

887
00:43:59.671 --> 00:44:02.007
* percussive. upbeat music *
